<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Code4SA Valentines</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/screen.css" media="screen, projection, handheld, tv">
	<script src="assets/js/polyfills/modernizr-custom.js"></script>
	<!--[if lte IE 8]><script src="assets/js/polyfills/respond.min.js"></script><![endif]-->
</head>
<body>

<div class="page-frame">
	<div class="layout">
		<div class="panel">
			<div class="panel-header">
				<h2>About you</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="panel-content">
				<label>Are you a man or woman?</label>
				<div class="binary-toggle">
					<div class="btoggle"><input type="radio" name="you-gender" value="woman" id="you-gender-woman" class="jsGenderToggle"><label for="you-gender-woman" class="woman">Woman</label></div>
					<div class="btoggle"><input type="radio" name="you-gender" value="man" id="you-gender-man" class="jsGenderToggle" checked="checked"><label for="you-gender-man" class="man">Man</label></div>
				</div>
				<label for="jsYouAge">How old are you?</label>
				<input type="range" class="range-slider" min="0" max="100" step="1" value="18" name="jsYouAge" id="jsYouAge" oninput="jsYouAgeOut.value = jsYouAge.value">
				<div class="tooltip-bubble"><output name="jsYouAgeOut" id="jsYouAgeOut">18</output></div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="icon-wedding-rings"></div>
		<div class="panel">
			<div class="panel-header">
				<h2>About your partner</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="panel-content">
				<label>Are you a man or woman?</label>
				<div class="binary-toggle">
					<div class="btoggle"><input type="radio" name="partner-gender" value="woman" id="partner-gender-woman" class="jsGenderToggle" checked="checked"><label for="partner-gender-woman" class="woman">Woman</label></div>
					<div class="btoggle"><input type="radio" name="partner-gender" value="man" id="partner-gender-man" class="jsGenderToggle"><label for="partner-gender-man" class="man">Man</label></div>
				</div>
				<label for="jsPartnerAge">How old is your partner?</label>
				<input type="range" class="range-slider" min="0" max="100" step="1" value="18" name="jsPartnerAge" id="jsPartnerAge" oninput="jsPartnerAgeOut.value = jsPartnerAge.value">
				<div class="tooltip-bubble"><output name="jsPartnerAgeOut" id="jsPartnerAgeOut">18</output></div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="panel panel-data">
			<div class="panel-header">
				<h2>What the data tells us</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="panel-content">
				<p><img src="assets/img/content/scorecard-3.png" alt="2nd most common age-pairing"></p>
				<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Quisque finibus posuere rhoncus. Nullam eleifend pulvinar diam at dictum. Integer tempus viverra mauris, et bibendum diam. Pellentesque aliquet imperdiet nunc, ac tempus eros elementum eu. Nullam finibus, sapien molestie iaculis posuere, tellus turpis interdum ipsum, quis molestie nunc.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<!-- loading CSS images at end of document as not essential to initial page load and render -->
<link href="assets/css/images.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" property="stylesheet">
<script src="assets/js/jquery.c4saValentines.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>